span class="token boolean important" style="color:#ff8b50;font-weight:400">false</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="클립보드에 코드 복사하기" title="복사" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><ol start="3"><li><code>-name: install app dependencies and build it</code> 바로 위에 다음 단계를 추가할 수 있습니다</li></ol><div class="language-yml codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:#282c34;--prism-color:#ffffff"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-yml codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#FAC863">name</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">:</span><span class="token plain"> import windows certificate</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#FAC863">if</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">:</span><span class="token plain"> matrix.platform == &#x27;windows</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">-</span><span class="token plain">latest&#x27;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#FAC863">env</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">:</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#FAC863">WINDOWS_CERTIFICATE</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">:</span><span class="token plain"> $</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">{</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">{</span><span class="token plain"> secrets.WINDOWS_CERTIFICATE </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">}</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#FAC863">WINDOWS_CERTIFICATE_PASSWORD</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">:</span><span class="token plain"> $</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">{</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">{</span><span class="token plain"> secrets.WINDOWS_CERTIFICATE_PASSWORD </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">}</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#FAC863">run</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#8dc891">|</span><span class="token scalar string" style="color:#8dc891"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token scalar string" style="color:#8dc891">    New-Item -ItemType directory -Path certificate</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token scalar string" style="color:#8dc891">    Set-Content -Path certificate/tempCert.txt -Value $env:WINDOWS_CERTIFICATE</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token scalar string" style="color:#8dc891">    certutil -decode certificate/tempCert.txt certificate/certificate.pfx</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token scalar string" style="color:#8dc891">    Remove-Item -path certificate -include tempCert.txt</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#ffffff"><span class="token scalar string" style="color:#8dc891">    Import-PfxCertificate -FilePath certificate/certificate.pfx -CertStoreLocation Cert:\CurrentUser\My -Password (ConvertTo-SecureString -String $env:WINDOWS_CERTIFICATE_PASSWORD -Force -AsPlainText)</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="클립보드에 코드 복사하기" title="복사" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><ol start="4"><li><p>저장 및 저장소에 푸시하기</p></li><li><p>Your workflow can now import your windows certificate and import it into the GitHub runner, allowing for automated code signing!</p></li></ol></div><footer class="theme-doc-footer docusaurus-mt-lg"><div class="theme-doc-footer-edit-meta-row row"><div class="col"><a href="https://github.com/tauri-apps/tauri-docs/edit/v1/docs/guides/distribution/sign-windows.md" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="theme-edit-this-page"><svg fill="currentColor" height="20" width="20" viewBox="0 0 40 40" class="iconEdit_Z9Sw" aria-hidden="true"><g><path d="m34.5 11.7l-3 3.1-6.3-6.3 3.1-3q0.5-0.5 1.2-0.5t1.1 0.5l3.9 3.9q0.5 0.4 0.5 1.1t-0.5 1.2z m-29.5 17.1l18.4-18.5 6.3 6.3-18.4 18.4h-6.3v-6.2z"></path></g></svg>이 페이지 편집</a></div><div class="col lastUpdated_vwxv"><span class="theme-last-updated"><b><time datetime="2023-05-29T11:40:57.000Z">2023년 5월 29일</time></b>에<!-- --> <!-- --> 마지막으로 갱신함</span></div></div></footer></article><nav class="pagination-nav docusaurus-mt-lg" aria-label="Docs pages"><a class="pagination-nav__link pagination-nav__link--prev" href="publishing"><div class="pagination-nav__sublabel">이전</div><div class="pagination-nav__label">앱 배포하기</div></a><a class="pagination-nav__link pagination-nav__link--next" href="sign-linux"><div class="pagination-nav__sublabel">다음</div><div class="pagination-nav__label">Linux 코드 서명</div></a></nav></div></div><div class="col col--3"><div class="tableOfContents_bqdL thin-scrollbar theme-doc-toc-desktop"><ul class="table-of-contents table-of-contents__left-border"><li><a href="sign-windows#소개" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">소개</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#사전-요구-사항" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">사전 요구 사항</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#시작하기" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">시작하기</a><ul><li><a href="sign-windows#a-cer-파일을-pfx로-전환하기" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">A. <code>.cer</code> 파일을 <code>.pfx</code>로 전환하기</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#b-키스토어에-pfx파일-불러오기" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">B. 키스토어에 <code>.pfx</code>파일 불러오기</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#c-변수-준비" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">C. 변수 준비</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="sign-windows#tauriconfjson파일-준비" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight"><code>tauri.conf.json</code>파일 준비</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#보너스-github-actions로-애플리케이션-서명" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">보너스: GitHub Actions로 애플리케이션 서명</a><ul><li><a href="sign-windows#github-secrets" class="table-of-contents__link toc-highlight">GitHub Secrets</a></li><li><a href="sign-windows#워크플로-수정" class=